<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_1869622_parkin_0_parking_reservation</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Create Jira Issue</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous) {
    
    try {
        // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ Jira Issue ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á
        if (current.getValue('jira_issue_key')) {
            gs.info('[Jira] Issue already exists: ' + current.getValue('jira_issue_key'));
            return;
        }
        
        // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ sync ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà
        if (current.getValue('sync_to_jira') != 'true') {
            gs.info('[Jira] Sync disabled for: ' + current.getValue('number'));
            return;
        }
        
        // ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á REST Message
        var restMessage = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('Jira Parking Integration', 'createParkingIssue');
        
        // ServiceNow URL
        var instanceUrl = gs.getProperty('glide.servlet.uri');
        var recordUrl = instanceUrl + 'x_1869622_parkin_0_parking_reservation.do?sys_id=' + current.sys_id;
        
        // ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Summary
        var summary = ']]>üÖø<![CDATA[Ô∏è Parking: ' + current.getValue('number') + ' - ' + 
                      current.requester_name.getDisplayValue();
        
        // ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Description (Jira Atlassian Document Format)
        var description = {
            "type": "doc",
            "version": 1,
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": { "level": 2 },
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "text": "Parking Reservation Details" }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Reservation Number: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.getValue('number') }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Requester: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.requester_name.getDisplayValue() }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Email: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.getValue('requester_email') }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Phone: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.getValue('requester_phone') }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "rule"
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": { "level": 3 },
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "text": "]]>üöó<![CDATA[ Vehicle Information" }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "License Plate: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.getValue('vehicle_registration_number') }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Car Type: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.getValue('car_type') }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "rule"
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": { "level": 3 },
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "text": "]]>üìÖ<![CDATA[ Booking Details" }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Start: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.start_date_time.getDisplayValue() }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "End: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.end_date_time.getDisplayValue() }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Duration: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.getValue('duration_hours') + ' hours' }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Location: " },
                        { "type": "text", "text": current.parking_location.getDisplayValue() }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "rule"
                },
                {
                    "type": "heading",
                    "attrs": { "level": 3 },
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "text": "]]>üí∞<![CDATA[ Payment" }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": "Fee: " },
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "strong" }], "text": current.getValue('parking_fee') + ' THB' }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "rule"
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": [
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "em" }], "text": "ServiceNow: " },
                        { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": recordUrl } }], "text": recordUrl }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        };
        
        // ‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏° Request Body
        var requestBody = {
            "fields": {
                "project": {
                    "key": "PARK"  // ‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô Project Key ‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì
                },
                "summary": summary,
                "description": description,
                "issuetype": {
                    "name": "Task"  // ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ "Story", "Bug" ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£
                },
                "priority": {
                    "name": "Medium"
                },
                "labels": [
                    "parking",
                    "reservation",
                    "servicenow"
                ]
            }
        };
        
        // ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á Request
        restMessage.setRequestBody(JSON.stringify(requestBody));
        var response = restMessage.execute();
        var responseBody = response.getBody();
        var statusCode = response.getStatusCode();
        
        // Log request
        gs.info('[Jira] Request sent for: ' + current.getValue('number'));
        gs.info('[Jira] Status Code: ' + statusCode);
        
        // ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏•‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ò‡πå
        if (statusCode == 201 || statusCode == 200) {
            var responseObj = JSON.parse(responseBody);
            var issueKey = responseObj.key;
            var issueId = responseObj.id;
            
            // ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Jira URL
            var jiraBaseUrl = 'https://mfec-team-eacabvze.atlassian.net';  // ‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô domain ‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á
            var issueUrl = jiraBaseUrl + '/browse/' + issueKey;
            
            // ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ô ServiceNow
            current.setValue('jira_issue_key', issueKey);
            current.setValue('jira_issue_url', issueUrl);
            current.setValue('jira_status', 'Open');
            current.update();
            
            // ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á Success Message
            gs.addInfoMessage('‚úì Jira issue created: ' + issueKey);
            gs.info('[Jira] Issue created successfully: ' + issueKey);
            
        } else {
            // Error handling
            gs.error('[Jira] Failed to create issue. Status: ' + statusCode);
            gs.error('[Jira] Response: ' + responseBody);
            gs.addErrorMessage('‚ùå Failed to create Jira issue. Check system logs.');
        }
        
    } catch (ex) {
        gs.error('[Jira] Exception: ' + ex.message);
        gs.logError(ex.message, 'Parking Jira Integration');
        gs.addErrorMessage('‚ùå Error creating Jira issue: ' + ex.message);
    }
    
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-12-18 03:25:39</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>2d96ec83c3717610ec76502ed4013190</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Create Jira Issue</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Parking Reservation System" source="x_1869622_parkin_0">6ea533f6c3adb290ec76502ed4013190</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Parking Reservation System">6ea533f6c3adb290ec76502ed4013190</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_2d96ec83c3717610ec76502ed4013190</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-12-18 03:25:39</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=2d96ec83c3717610ec76502ed4013190"/></record_update>
